            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> on a large plate</p><p>Add the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1] </span><strong>lemon</strong> to a bowl with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give it a good mix up until the lemon and oil have combined - this is your <strong>lemon & olive oil mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-copy-2-1636448536816-x200.jpg",
