            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dip the<strong> flattened</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>breasts</strong> in the<strong> lemon & olive oil mix</strong> then press firmly into the<strong> panko breadcrumbs</strong> until both sides are evenly coated</p><p>Add the<strong> coated</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> to one side of an oiled baking tray</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
