            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cherry tomatoes </strong>to the other side of the baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the tomatoes have started to blister and char</p>",
      "order": 5,
