          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash the <strong>baby kale </strong>then add it to a <strong>food processor</strong></p><p>Peel the <strong>garlic</strong> and grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> garlic </strong>(not a fan of raw garlic? Go easy!), the <strong>grated cheddar</strong>, <strong>walnuts</strong>, 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, the juice of the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon</strong> and 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span> <strong>salt</strong> to the <strong>food processor</strong></p><p>Whizz it all up until blitzed but not smooth and set aside – this is your <strong>baby</strong> <strong>kale pesto</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
