            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, drain the <strong>potatoes</strong> and return them to the pot with a large knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Mash them until smooth</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>baby</strong> <strong>kale pesto</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) to the pot, then mix to combine – this is your <strong>green mash</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-copy-2-1636448568997-x200.jpg",
